nodes.text: Dinni Dusko was a male resident of Theed who lived during the time of the Galactic Civil War.

Dialogue pertaining to Dinni Dusko appeared in the directory tree files for the 2003 massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided. However, the quest he was mentioned in never actually appeared on the video game's live servers.
